Bringing Californian Almonds from farms in California to you

  • 3 Friends
  • 1500+ acres of farms in California
  • 3 Million pounds of almond produce a year
  • Hassle-free delivery with no intermediary

This is our story,in a nutshell.

We saw a problem, we made it ours...

Fresh, farm-picked almonds are often passed between dozens of hands at harvest, and travel thousands of miles across various intermediaries.

They see multiple shipping vehicles, retail warehouses, re-packaging shop floors and delivery fleets before they reach the retail stores.

This is bound to affect the quality and price.

We wished for Ramara to be the solution. We made it happen!

HERE'S HOW!

We bring best quality almonds at the best price, straight from our Californian farms, with a strategically improvised supply chain management, that cuts down on all intermediaries.

We are committed to provide the best-quality almonds with delightful taste and the best possible price!

And, we would like to do business with you.

The Ramara Promise

Of Experience, Ethics & a Decade’s FriendshipMeet The faces behind Ramara

30 years ago, the three of us vowed to do great things together. Sticking on to that, we have set feet into the almonds business, with a dream to bring high-quality almonds straight from our farms, directly to the consumers, through YOU!

Mohamed Jahir HussainManaging Director at Ramara

25+ years of experience in Business Management, Real Estate, Distribution Business, Manufacturing, Import & Export, Distribution Marketing & Distribution Channels. Started his entrepreneurial career in 1991, becoming the distributor for Hindustan Lever’s product line for two districts in Southern India. The business produced ₹ 93 lakhs per month, covering 1600 outlets. Managing Director/Partner of NaRDil Enterprise, a construction-support service company, for 13+ years. Instrumental in growing NaRDil from a small group of 15 people to a large 250-people enterprise.

Aravindhan ThayaparanDirector at Ramara

Senior Executive at a leading Technology firm in California! 25+ years of experience in Executive Management, Heavy Commercial Construction, Worldwide Retail Experience, Global Knowledge, & Strategic Thinking. Co-Founding Partner of Ramara Farms LLC (established 2018) operating over 1,500 Acres of almonds & walnuts. Senior Executive for Global Retail Store Development at a leading Technology company headquartered in California.

Ramesh NagarajahDirector at Ramara

Comes with a vast knowledge in Global Business Development, Strategy, Mentoring, Marketing, Sales, & Client Relationships. Founder & Chairman of NaRDil Enterprise (established in 2005), a successful 250-people construction-support service company operating. Sprouting from a successful global farming family, thoroughly familiar with the characteristics of the Almond and Walnut plants, its generation and growth, the diseases and blights to which it is susceptible, and the methods of controlling them, to produce a quality product.
